\begin{problem}
\begin{enumerate}
        \item  For a flow with constant bit rate $c$, give some
        possible arrival curves.
        \item  Consider a flow with an arrival curve given by: $\alpha(t)=B$,
        where $B$ is constant. What does this mean for the flow ?
\end{enumerate}
\end{problem}
